name: Spherical Ears
description:
***Free Shipping now and always***

My all time favorite earrings to wear!

These domed sterling silver earrings measure just under 1.5 cm through the center and have sterling silver ear posts soldered to the back. I brought the front to a very nice organic/matte finish while the back is a high polish finish. These are 100% handmade and come with sterling silver earring backs.
Yours might vary slightly from the picture due to being handmade but will be made especially for you....Enjoy the uniqueness.

name: Black Hearts Burn
description:
A small statement indicating you aren't so average.... Like the authentic, not-so-average Black Diamond that sits nicely in it's tube setting

This ring is a size 3 3/4 (3.75) with a tube set 2.9mmm genuine Black Diamond (0.09 carat). The ring shank is brushed/matte sterling silver and is approximately 1.75mm wide
The brushed texture of the silver makes the diamond really stand out.

Look for other rings in different sizes with different stones coming soon

One of a kind


This makes a beautiful pinky ring

name: Going to Town
description:
*****FREE SHIPPING NOW AND ALWAYS*****

A few dandelions or poppies (if that's what you see) hanging around, waiting to be blown away. This piece is completely hand sawed and hung from an 18" sterling silver by a handmade bail.
The disc is approximately 1" through the center.


**As your jewelry will be handmade especially for you when ordered, please allow some mild but original differences**

name: Mmmm Chocolate
description:
***Free Shipping now and always!!***

My favorite stone by far. The Chocolate or Cognac Diamond. This is a 2.7 mm authentic Chocolate Diamond that has been tube set in Sterling Silver. I've made this ring in a soft-square shape. The most comfortable shape for the base of the finger. The band is 1.75mm thick and the ring is size 5.5

This can be brushed finished (as seen in the pictures) or can be brought to a high polish finish

One of a kind

name: Salix Discolor
description:
****FREE SHIPPING NOW AND ALWAYS*****

Just another name for Pussy Willows :)
This is a different take on my other round pussy willow piece. Two tall mismatched stems adorn this rectangle slab hanging by 2 sterling silver, handmade bails on a 16" Sterling silver chain.
All hand cut, pierced, sawed and finished by me.
Measures around 1" tall by .5" wide

If you would like a different length chain please let me know in the "note to seller" area when you purchase your item.
